    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>It would be possible to interpret χρυσίον in {S:06601700400022} as being merely a natural substance and thus classified with χρυσίον[a] ({D:2.49}), but χρυσίον[b] seems to have acquired certain specializations of meaning and even in the singular to be a collective for objects made of gold. It is for that reason that χρυσίον in {S:06601700400022} is classified in this domain.</Content>
    </Note>
